3 types of control flow statements
1. Decision Making Statements
        - if statement
            a) Simple if
            b) if-else
            c) if-else-if ladder
            d) Nested if
        - switch statement
            - executes one statement from multiple condition
            - works with byte,short,int,long(till Java 6)
            - works with String(From Java 7)
2. Loop Statements
        - for loop
            a)Simple for loop
            b)Nested for loop
        - while loop
        - do while loop
        - for each loop
3. Jump Statements
        - break statement
        - continue statement

